oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Corner of 10th Avenue South and Archer Street, 1965
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the southwest corner of 10th Avenue South and Archer Street. The area was part of the Edgehill Urban Renewal Project (Project Tenn. R-69). Photographed by Bill Driver of the Nashville Housing Authority, 13 May 1965. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
